1
00:01:34,140 --> 00:01:37,460
[Episode 13]

2
00:01:37,460 --> 00:01:39,100
Fan.

3
00:01:39,100 --> 00:01:40,932
Has the world...

4
00:01:41,500 --> 00:01:43,749
gone mad?

5
00:02:00,179 --> 00:02:02,670
I'm so tired.

6
00:02:02,670 --> 00:02:04,345
Fan.

7
00:02:07,460 --> 00:02:10,582
I haven't been this tired in a long time.

8
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:23,385
[Shangqing Hall]

9
00:02:43,660 --> 00:02:45,722
Master Ding.

10
00:02:46,495 --> 00:02:49,157
Why are you here, Master Ding?

11
00:02:50,219 --> 00:02:51,780
Mrs. Jing.

12
00:02:51,780 --> 00:02:54,939
I was just taking a walk to clear my head.

13
00:02:54,939 --> 00:02:56,700
If you wish to clear your head,

14
00:02:56,700 --> 00:02:59,020
the front garden would be better.

15
00:02:59,020 --> 00:03:00,632
I see.

16
00:03:08,019 --> 00:03:10,420
You should avoid this area.

17
00:03:10,420 --> 00:03:12,299
If Master Jing sees you,

18
00:03:12,299 --> 00:03:14,500
he will suspect you.

19
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:16,307
Mrs. Jing.

20
00:03:20,579 --> 00:03:23,579
You said Uncle Jing will suspect me.

21
00:03:23,579 --> 00:03:25,682
Suspect me of what?

22
00:03:27,900 --> 00:03:30,132
Do you know something?

23
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:46,500
My Lord.

24
00:03:46,500 --> 00:03:48,295
Uncle Jing.

25
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:54,182
Nephew, why have you come here?

26
00:03:54,182 --> 00:03:56,419
Well, I just came out for a walk.

27
00:03:56,419 --> 00:03:58,420
I'm not familiar with
the layout of the Jing house.

28
00:03:58,420 --> 00:04:00,979
I just ended up here while wandering.

29
00:04:00,979 --> 00:04:04,165
Since you moved in, I have been quite busy.

30
00:04:04,165 --> 00:04:05,939
Sorry, I've neglected you.

31
00:04:05,939 --> 00:04:07,539
Uncle Jing, why would you say that?

32
00:04:07,539 --> 00:04:09,859
You let me stay here to help me find someone.

33
00:04:09,859 --> 00:04:11,220
I'm already imposing on you.

34
00:04:11,220 --> 00:04:12,740
Don't say that.

35
00:04:12,740 --> 00:04:14,460
Your family has faced such trouble,

36
00:04:14,460 --> 00:04:17,020
yet you came all this way
to celebrate my birthday.

37
00:04:17,020 --> 00:04:20,060
Such sincerity is truly rare to me.

38
00:04:20,060 --> 00:04:23,620
Speaking of which,
your father and I are the same age.

39
00:04:23,620 --> 00:04:25,500
As my birthday approaches,

40
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:27,220
these past few days...

41
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:29,895
I find myself thinking of him often.

42
00:04:29,895 --> 00:04:31,339
Well, Uncle Jing.

43
00:04:31,339 --> 00:04:33,700
The big day is almost here.

44
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:36,154
Let's not dwell on sad things.

45
00:04:36,866 --> 00:04:39,420
Alright. Come here.

46
00:04:39,420 --> 00:04:41,702
I've seen you out and about lately.

47
00:04:41,702 --> 00:04:44,401
Any news on Yue Hua's whereabouts?

48
00:04:45,180 --> 00:04:46,900
No news yet.

49
00:04:46,900 --> 00:04:51,045
I've sent men to search the nearby counties,
but they found nothing.

50
00:04:51,045 --> 00:04:55,219
I'm just worried that she'll cause trouble
at the Shangqing Sect during your banquet,

51
00:04:55,219 --> 00:04:57,420
ruining the banquet.

52
00:04:57,420 --> 00:04:59,219
Forget about the banquet.

53
00:04:59,219 --> 00:05:00,580
Put all that aside.

54
00:05:00,580 --> 00:05:02,260
It would be better if she did show up.

55
00:05:02,260 --> 00:05:06,260
At least then, we would have news of her.

56
00:05:06,260 --> 00:05:07,580
Let's not talk about this anymore.

57
00:05:07,580 --> 00:05:10,570
- I'll walk with you.
- Alright.

58
00:05:15,580 --> 00:05:17,420
Uncle Jing, I'll take my leave now.

59
00:05:17,420 --> 00:05:18,970
Alright.

60
00:05:24,659 --> 00:05:26,307
Thank you.

61
00:05:38,219 --> 00:05:39,339
Father.

62
00:05:39,339 --> 00:05:40,779
How long is Ding Zhao Hui...

63
00:05:40,779 --> 00:05:42,420
going to stay at our house?

64
00:05:42,420 --> 00:05:43,740
Aren't you going to send him away?

65
00:05:43,740 --> 00:05:45,220
He's just a fool.

66
00:05:45,220 --> 00:05:46,859
Is he an eyesore to you?

67
00:05:46,859 --> 00:05:48,260
I was just thinking.

68
00:05:48,260 --> 00:05:50,179
With all the trouble the Ding family is in,

69
00:05:50,179 --> 00:05:52,833
he is still in the mood
to celebrate your birthday.

70
00:05:52,833 --> 00:05:54,747
Something seems fishy.

71
00:05:54,747 --> 00:05:56,579
I have my suspicions as well.

72
00:05:56,579 --> 00:06:00,900
After he arrived,
I sent men to investigate his family.

73
00:06:00,900 --> 00:06:04,020
Ding Zhao Lan is indeed in a coma,
just as he said.

74
00:06:04,020 --> 00:06:06,500
Ding Yue Hua hasn't returned home either.

75
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:08,940
However, we cannot let our guard down.

76
00:06:08,940 --> 00:06:10,979
Since his intentions are unclear,

77
00:06:10,979 --> 00:06:14,282
I must keep him here.

78
00:06:14,282 --> 00:06:16,340
Keep him right under our noses.

79
00:06:16,340 --> 00:06:19,940
If anything goes wrong,
we can finish him off immediately.

80
00:06:20,932 --> 00:06:23,979
I've seen him wandering around
the backyard lately.

81
00:06:23,979 --> 00:06:27,059
Tell your men to keep a close
watch on that small backyard.

82
00:06:27,059 --> 00:06:28,140
Don't let him get near it.

83
00:06:28,140 --> 00:06:29,539
Yes, Father.

84
00:06:29,539 --> 00:06:32,670
That room is currently guarded day and night.

85
00:06:32,670 --> 00:06:34,099
But speaking of which,

86
00:06:34,099 --> 00:06:36,340
Ding Yue Hua's disappearance is strange.

87
00:06:36,340 --> 00:06:38,060
Where could she have gone?

88
00:06:38,060 --> 00:06:42,083
Could she really come for revenge
during the birthday banquet?

89
00:06:42,083 --> 00:06:44,246
Why do you care?

90
00:06:44,246 --> 00:06:45,900
If she doesn't come, fine.

91
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:48,632
If she does, she's a dead woman!

92
00:06:53,299 --> 00:06:56,539
You should focus
on managing Zhongxiao Pavilion.

93
00:06:56,539 --> 00:06:59,320
That Hua Chong is one of your men, right?

94
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:01,420
I only recruited him
because he knew so many girls.

95
00:07:01,420 --> 00:07:02,500
That's why...

96
00:07:02,500 --> 00:07:04,220
Remember this.

97
00:07:04,220 --> 00:07:07,900
From now on, you must never use
low-life thugs like him again.

98
00:07:07,900 --> 00:07:09,620
Yes.

99
00:07:09,620 --> 00:07:11,739
Now that Hua Chong is in Zhan Zhao's custody,

100
00:07:11,739 --> 00:07:14,299
silencing him will be very difficult.

101
00:07:14,299 --> 00:07:16,419
Also, regarding the matter of
the Yicheng County Magistrate,

102
00:07:16,419 --> 00:07:17,739
we didn't succeed there either.

103
00:07:17,739 --> 00:07:20,007
I am truly anxious.

104
00:07:20,007 --> 00:07:22,859
But Zhi Hua isn't worried at all.

105
00:07:22,859 --> 00:07:25,179
He said he has a way
to solve the current crisis.

106
00:07:25,179 --> 00:07:27,460
When I asked him how, he wouldn't say.

107
00:07:27,460 --> 00:07:31,340
Father, now is not the time to let him
do things his own way.

108
00:07:31,340 --> 00:07:34,820
Since he said he has a way,
then let's wait for his news.

109
00:07:34,820 --> 00:07:36,739
He handled things well this time.

110
00:07:36,739 --> 00:07:38,900
But look at you, you're too impulsive.

111
00:07:38,900 --> 00:07:40,299
If you keep this up,

112
00:07:40,299 --> 00:07:42,460
how will you command respect
in Zhongxiao Pavilion?

113
00:07:42,460 --> 00:07:43,739
Then so be it.

114
00:07:43,739 --> 00:07:45,099
With Zhi Hua around,

115
00:07:45,099 --> 00:07:47,795
I have no say in Zhongxiao Pavilion anyway.

116
00:07:51,859 --> 00:07:54,220
Shut your mouth!

117
00:07:54,220 --> 00:07:57,059
You are the rightful heir
of our Shangqing Sect.

118
00:07:57,059 --> 00:07:59,940
Stop saying such pathetic things!

119
00:07:59,940 --> 00:08:02,739
The trouble Liu Hong Yi caused
has only just settled,

120
00:08:02,739 --> 00:08:04,539
and now something's come wrong again.

121
00:08:04,539 --> 00:08:07,380
Pull yourself together and keep
a close eye on Zhongxiao Pavilion!

122
00:08:07,380 --> 00:08:09,059
If anything else goes wrong,

123
00:08:09,059 --> 00:08:11,979
you'll have to answer to His Lordship yourself!

124
00:08:11,979 --> 00:08:13,545
Yes, Father.

125
00:08:47,833 --> 00:08:49,539
Bai.

126
00:08:49,539 --> 00:08:51,295
You're awake.

127
00:08:52,936 --> 00:08:54,380
The medicine will be ready soon.

128
00:08:54,380 --> 00:08:57,340
After you drink it, we'll go meet
Zhan as soon as possible.

129
00:08:57,340 --> 00:08:58,900
The rain is getting heavier.

130
00:08:58,900 --> 00:09:00,920
Don't keep him waiting.

131
00:09:02,940 --> 00:09:05,460
Since I arrived in Xiangzhou,

132
00:09:06,420 --> 00:09:09,500
I've heard many stories about the Yaksha.

133
00:09:10,499 --> 00:09:13,370
They have told me a lot,

134
00:09:13,370 --> 00:09:15,890
and taught me many lessons.

135
00:09:16,660 --> 00:09:18,260
Just drink the medicine first.

136
00:09:18,260 --> 00:09:21,307
We can't send Fan off just like this.

137
00:09:24,380 --> 00:09:25,940
To pay respects to Fan,

138
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:28,034
we still need some offerings.

139
00:09:28,900 --> 00:09:32,420
Offerings? Zhan has prepared everything.

140
00:09:32,420 --> 00:09:34,220
No.

141
00:09:35,619 --> 00:09:38,170
We're still missing the most important one.

142
00:09:38,170 --> 00:09:39,845
Bai!

143
00:09:40,539 --> 00:09:41,739
Step aside.

144
00:09:41,739 --> 00:09:43,020
You're no match for me.

145
00:09:43,020 --> 00:09:44,059
He can't die.

146
00:09:44,059 --> 00:09:46,657
If Fan were still here, he wouldn't want--

147
00:09:49,340 --> 00:09:51,340
But he's gone.

148
00:09:52,340 --> 00:09:54,380
I'm sorry.

149
00:09:54,380 --> 00:09:57,332
Your acupoints will release on their own.

150
00:09:59,860 --> 00:10:02,757
Master Bai, please don't!

151
00:10:10,140 --> 00:10:12,859
Don't worry. I won't kill you.

152
00:10:13,859 --> 00:10:15,700
You don't deserve to die by my hand.

153
00:10:15,700 --> 00:10:18,475
And I won't let you off that easily.

154
00:10:24,899 --> 00:10:26,957
Zhi Hua!

155
00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:29,980
Zhi Hua!

156
00:10:29,980 --> 00:10:31,900
Come out!

157
00:10:47,300 --> 00:10:50,780
Our appointed time hasn't arrived yet.

158
00:10:50,780 --> 00:10:52,660
Why are you in such a hurry to find me?

159
00:10:52,660 --> 00:10:54,099
I know.

160
00:10:54,099 --> 00:10:55,979
You're anxious to kill him to keep him quiet.

161
00:10:55,979 --> 00:10:57,220
I've brought the man to you.

162
00:10:57,220 --> 00:10:59,770
Consider it a gesture of sincerity
for the antidote.

163
00:11:05,460 --> 00:11:07,499
A scoundrel like you...

164
00:11:07,499 --> 00:11:08,980
I'm afraid that when you fell into Zhan Zhao,

165
00:11:08,980 --> 00:11:12,267
you'd spill everything
about Zhongxiao Pavilion.

166
00:11:13,499 --> 00:11:15,139
He didn't say a word.

167
00:11:15,139 --> 00:11:16,733
Before he could open his mouth,

168
00:11:16,733 --> 00:11:18,140
I fed him something.

169
00:11:18,140 --> 00:11:19,660
Good.

170
00:11:19,660 --> 00:11:22,460
Your medicine was given just in time.

171
00:11:22,460 --> 00:11:24,739
Now that he's mute,

172
00:11:24,739 --> 00:11:26,259
I have no choice but to believe you.

173
00:11:26,259 --> 00:11:28,672
You've already killed Clerk Fang and Fan.

174
00:11:28,672 --> 00:11:30,213
Now that I've brought him here too,

175
00:11:30,213 --> 00:11:32,407
are you still not satisfied?

176
00:11:47,099 --> 00:11:48,500
Give me the antidote.

177
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:51,707
From the very beginning,
I never asked you for Hua Chong.

178
00:11:51,707 --> 00:11:55,260
What I want is information
on Zhan Zhao's investigation.

179
00:11:55,260 --> 00:11:58,260
Hua Chong didn't confess anything
before I brought him here.

180
00:11:58,260 --> 00:12:01,340
This has already blocked
Zhan Zhao's path of investigation.

181
00:12:01,340 --> 00:12:03,155
Not enough.

182
00:12:10,019 --> 00:12:11,980
You want to fight?

183
00:12:11,980 --> 00:12:13,380
Fine.

184
00:12:13,380 --> 00:12:15,020
Come on.

185
00:12:15,020 --> 00:12:17,260
I'll trade my one life

186
00:12:17,260 --> 00:12:18,980
for the lives of your two sworn brothers.

187
00:12:18,980 --> 00:12:21,105
See if you think it's worth it.

188
00:12:30,860 --> 00:12:32,755
Zhan Zhao is here.

189
00:12:43,380 --> 00:12:45,580
Bai Yu Tang is here too.

190
00:12:45,580 --> 00:12:48,455
You don't have to make a move.

191
00:12:53,179 --> 00:12:55,060
You're a step too late.

192
00:12:55,060 --> 00:12:57,855
Hua Chong is already dead.

193
00:13:02,940 --> 00:13:04,740
I didn't come here to save Hua Chong.

194
00:13:04,740 --> 00:13:06,220
I came to save you!

195
00:13:06,220 --> 00:13:08,539
Save me?

196
00:13:08,539 --> 00:13:10,685
I don't need your saving.

197
00:13:10,685 --> 00:13:13,779
No one in this world can tell me what to do.

198
00:13:13,779 --> 00:13:18,139
Whatever I set out to do,
I will see it through to the end.

199
00:13:18,139 --> 00:13:19,659
Dealing with the devil

200
00:13:19,659 --> 00:13:21,179
will not end well.

201
00:13:21,179 --> 00:13:22,299
Come back with me.

202
00:13:22,299 --> 00:13:23,539
Regarding Fan's matter,

203
00:13:23,539 --> 00:13:24,939
I will definitely give you an answer!

204
00:13:24,939 --> 00:13:27,700
I'm not the one you need to answer to!

205
00:13:27,700 --> 00:13:31,500
Zhan Zhao, if you still insist on following
your ridiculous official rules,

206
00:13:31,500 --> 00:13:34,330
then from now on,
we have nothing to do with each other!

207
00:13:34,330 --> 00:13:36,347
Step aside!

208
00:13:41,779 --> 00:13:43,260
Zhan Zhao,

209
00:13:43,260 --> 00:13:45,380
don't force my hand.

210
00:13:48,419 --> 00:13:50,369
Step aside!

211
00:14:14,740 --> 00:14:16,692
Have you had enough?

212
00:14:18,659 --> 00:14:21,192
Wait for me at Fan's grave.

213
00:14:46,019 --> 00:14:47,299
Fan.

214
00:14:47,299 --> 00:14:50,178
[Tomb of Fan Zhong Yu, The Song Hermit]
I brought Hua Chong to atone for his crimes.

215
00:14:50,178 --> 00:14:51,740
He died a very painful death.

216
00:14:51,740 --> 00:14:54,130
If you can hear me from the afterlife,

217
00:14:54,740 --> 00:14:56,517
you can rest in peace now.

218
00:14:56,517 --> 00:14:58,980
Once the case is closed,

219
00:14:58,980 --> 00:15:01,899
Hua Chong would have naturally
faced the judgment he deserved.

220
00:15:01,899 --> 00:15:03,779
Why couldn't you just wait?

221
00:15:03,779 --> 00:15:05,505
Wait?

222
00:15:07,105 --> 00:15:09,139
Why should I wait?

223
00:15:09,139 --> 00:15:10,500
Wait until when?

224
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:12,500
He had to die right now!

225
00:15:12,500 --> 00:15:13,860
To pay for Fan's life.

226
00:15:13,860 --> 00:15:17,460
For Hui Dai, and for all the girls
in Zhongxiao Pavilion!

227
00:15:17,460 --> 00:15:22,967
My only regret now is that I didn't kill him
while Fan was still alive.

228
00:15:28,740 --> 00:15:33,059
In Xiangzhou,
everyone worships Yaksha as a god.

229
00:15:34,059 --> 00:15:36,330
Do you know why?

230
00:15:36,330 --> 00:15:39,100
Because the government
can't give the people justice.

231
00:15:39,100 --> 00:15:42,700
They can only place their hope in Yaksha.

232
00:15:42,700 --> 00:15:45,700
Kaifeng Prefecture is indeed different
from those corrupt offices.

233
00:15:45,700 --> 00:15:47,260
But what's the use?

234
00:15:47,260 --> 00:15:49,980
Even if Lord Bao is known as Justice
and judges cases like a god,

235
00:15:49,980 --> 00:15:53,500
can he handle every injustice in this world?

236
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:56,419
The corruption in Xiangzhou's officialdom
didn't just happen overnight.

237
00:15:56,419 --> 00:16:01,100
Lord of Xiangyang has dominated
Xiangzhou for over ten years.

238
00:16:01,100 --> 00:16:04,019
I don't believe that no word of this
ever reached the imperial court.

239
00:16:04,019 --> 00:16:05,899
After ten years of this mess,

240
00:16:05,899 --> 00:16:07,779
they sent only you, Zhan Zhao.

241
00:16:07,779 --> 00:16:12,260
Do they believe a fourth-rank officer like you
can completely wipe out his power?

242
00:16:12,260 --> 00:16:15,539
Or do they just not value your life?

243
00:16:15,539 --> 00:16:17,045
Don't you understand yet?

244
00:16:17,045 --> 00:16:19,620
They sent you here just to go through
the motions.

245
00:16:19,620 --> 00:16:21,659
It's all just a show for the people.

246
00:16:21,659 --> 00:16:23,460
Of all these matters,

247
00:16:23,460 --> 00:16:26,019
how much do you see clearly?

248
00:16:26,019 --> 00:16:27,260
People living in the world

249
00:16:27,260 --> 00:16:29,220
mock you as a dog of the imperial court.

250
00:16:29,220 --> 00:16:32,659
The court ministers look down on you
for your humble origins.

251
00:16:32,659 --> 00:16:34,539
The world is vast, and the court is wide,

252
00:16:34,539 --> 00:16:37,492
but is there any place for you?

253
00:16:43,020 --> 00:16:46,740
I think Yaksha might truly exist.

254
00:16:46,740 --> 00:16:48,260
But he is not a god.

255
00:16:48,260 --> 00:16:51,367
He is a hero who slays all evil.

256
00:16:54,740 --> 00:16:57,667
I quite like the title of Yaksha.

257
00:16:59,019 --> 00:17:00,260
Zhan Zhao,

258
00:17:00,260 --> 00:17:02,779
become Yaksha with me.

259
00:17:02,779 --> 00:17:06,392
Let's be the judges of this filthy world
together.

260
00:17:18,260 --> 00:17:21,059
I like your title of Yaksha.

261
00:17:21,059 --> 00:17:22,899
No matter what I do,

262
00:17:22,899 --> 00:17:25,139
if it's done by the Yaksha,

263
00:17:25,139 --> 00:17:28,139
everyone says "Well done"
and "You did the right thing."

264
00:17:28,139 --> 00:17:31,019
Since this title of Yaksha
is so convenient,

265
00:17:31,019 --> 00:17:33,767
then anyone can use it.

266
00:17:41,540 --> 00:17:42,899
You have truly gone mad!

267
00:17:42,899 --> 00:17:44,980
Is it you who's mad, or is it me?

268
00:17:44,980 --> 00:17:46,900
I kill evil men. What have I done wrong?

269
00:17:46,900 --> 00:17:49,179
Fighting violence with violence is not justice.

270
00:17:49,179 --> 00:17:51,020
And slaughter is never a virtuous act!

271
00:17:51,020 --> 00:17:52,780
Blood for blood, an eye for an eye.

272
00:17:52,780 --> 00:17:54,579
That has always been my way!

273
00:17:54,579 --> 00:17:57,492
Only because I met my sworn brothers that I--

274
00:18:01,099 --> 00:18:02,655
Forget it.

275
00:18:02,655 --> 00:18:04,900
Since Lord Zhan, you despise my methods,

276
00:18:04,900 --> 00:18:06,739
then we shall go our separate ways.

277
00:18:06,739 --> 00:18:08,219
From this day forward,

278
00:18:08,219 --> 00:18:10,992
we shall mind our own business.

279
00:18:17,219 --> 00:18:19,099
Zhan Zhao, remember this.

280
00:18:19,099 --> 00:18:20,699
At least for now,

281
00:18:20,699 --> 00:18:24,180
the one who made Hua Chong kneel and
repent at Fan's grave

282
00:18:24,180 --> 00:18:26,500
was not the government.

283
00:18:26,500 --> 00:18:28,892
It was I, Bai Yu Tang.

284
00:18:48,380 --> 00:18:49,660
In this world,

285
00:18:49,660 --> 00:18:51,660
if justice truly existed,

286
00:18:51,660 --> 00:18:54,367
how could someone like me...

287
00:18:54,367 --> 00:18:58,580
have become a government official?

288
00:19:01,219 --> 00:19:02,539
Lord Zhan,

289
00:19:02,539 --> 00:19:06,140
you insist on seeking justice.

290
00:19:06,140 --> 00:19:07,660
Let me give you some advice.

291
00:19:07,660 --> 00:19:11,940
Don't be like your short-lived brother,

292
00:19:11,940 --> 00:19:16,217
only realizing when death is near
that the road ahead...

293
00:19:16,217 --> 00:19:19,305
is a dead end.

294
00:19:24,299 --> 00:19:27,059
The corruption in Xiangzhou's officialdom
didn't just happen overnight.

295
00:19:27,059 --> 00:19:31,059
Lord of Xiangyang has dominated
Xiangzhou for over ten years.

296
00:19:31,059 --> 00:19:32,860
After ten years of this mess,

297
00:19:32,860 --> 00:19:34,739
they sent only you, Zhan Zhao.

298
00:19:34,739 --> 00:19:39,180
Do they believe a fourth-rank officer like
you can completely wipe out his power?

299
00:19:39,180 --> 00:19:41,876
Or do they just not value your life?

300
00:19:42,579 --> 00:19:43,860
People living in the world

301
00:19:43,860 --> 00:19:45,819
mock you as a dog of the imperial court.

302
00:19:45,819 --> 00:19:49,259
The court ministers look down on you
for your humble origins.

303
00:19:49,259 --> 00:19:51,180
The world is vast,
and the court is wide,

304
00:19:51,180 --> 00:19:54,003
but is there any place for you?

305
00:19:59,420 --> 00:20:00,739
Zhan Zhao,

306
00:20:00,739 --> 00:20:03,255
become Yaksha with me.

307
00:20:03,255 --> 00:20:07,005
Let's be the judges
of this filthy world.

308
00:20:23,700 --> 00:20:26,055
Are you all right, Zhan?

309
00:20:53,940 --> 00:20:55,259
To be honest,

310
00:20:55,259 --> 00:20:56,660
in all my years,

311
00:20:56,660 --> 00:21:00,019
I've never seen such a terrifying case.

312
00:21:00,019 --> 00:21:02,819
Nor have I ever seen
such terrifying human hearts.

313
00:21:02,819 --> 00:21:04,979
Last night,

314
00:21:04,979 --> 00:21:08,248
I even thought about
returning to Linglong Manor.

315
00:21:10,292 --> 00:21:12,948
But I thought about it all night
and I understand now.

316
00:21:13,605 --> 00:21:15,645
Everything I'm facing now

317
00:21:15,645 --> 00:21:19,213
is a necessary experience
for my journey in the world.

318
00:21:24,339 --> 00:21:26,019
Zhan,

319
00:21:27,019 --> 00:21:29,700
no matter how hard the road ahead is,

320
00:21:29,700 --> 00:21:31,755
we will eventually reach the end.

321
00:21:35,380 --> 00:21:37,900
This case has vast implications.

322
00:21:37,900 --> 00:21:39,900
The further we investigate,

323
00:21:39,900 --> 00:21:42,555
the more dangerous it will become.

324
00:21:42,555 --> 00:21:44,700
- Miss Huo, you should--
- Zhan.

325
00:21:44,700 --> 00:21:46,940
What I meant just now was,

326
00:21:46,940 --> 00:21:48,967
no matter how difficult it gets,

327
00:21:48,967 --> 00:21:51,259
I will see this through with you.

328
00:21:51,259 --> 00:21:52,673
Look.

329
00:21:52,673 --> 00:21:54,539
My skills aren't bad either.

330
00:21:54,539 --> 00:21:56,019
I can protect others,

331
00:21:56,019 --> 00:21:58,020
and I can protect myself.

332
00:21:58,020 --> 00:21:59,500
I'll investigate the case with you

333
00:21:59,500 --> 00:22:01,180
and protect you by your side.

334
00:22:01,180 --> 00:22:03,192
Isn't that good?

335
00:22:05,980 --> 00:22:07,020
Enough.

336
00:22:07,020 --> 00:22:08,460
If you keep going,

337
00:22:08,460 --> 00:22:11,855
I'll think you're underestimating me,
just like Shao Ji Zu did.

338
00:22:21,619 --> 00:22:23,355
Tell me,

339
00:22:24,180 --> 00:22:26,967
everything we're doing now...

340
00:22:27,780 --> 00:22:29,730
Liu...

341
00:22:29,730 --> 00:22:31,905
Fan...

342
00:22:31,905 --> 00:22:34,625
and the girls who died in Zhongxiao Pavilion...

343
00:22:34,625 --> 00:22:37,030
can they see it?

344
00:22:38,700 --> 00:22:40,619
I'm just afraid.

345
00:22:40,619 --> 00:22:44,880
I'm afraid that the justice we seek
is a justice that has come too late.

346
00:22:46,180 --> 00:22:49,242
Everything we're doing now...

347
00:22:50,859 --> 00:22:53,180
is actually too late.

348
00:22:54,180 --> 00:22:56,260
Zhan.

349
00:22:56,260 --> 00:22:58,455
Let me take you somewhere.

350
00:23:00,020 --> 00:23:02,067
Wonderful!

351
00:23:03,339 --> 00:23:05,355
Wonderful!

352
00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:22,367
Look at this street.
How is it different from before?

353
00:23:24,980 --> 00:23:28,460
When we first came here, it was empty.

354
00:23:28,460 --> 00:23:33,553
I suppose the embroidery shop owner didn't
allow them to set up stalls here.

355
00:23:34,379 --> 00:23:37,220
But now that the shop is closed.

356
00:23:37,220 --> 00:23:38,579
Look.

357
00:23:38,579 --> 00:23:42,442
That old lady can sell
her silk threads here now.

358
00:23:43,900 --> 00:23:45,273
Tell me,

359
00:23:45,273 --> 00:23:47,460
if the embroidery shop hadn't closed,

360
00:23:47,460 --> 00:23:50,859
would those two girls
have walked into that shop?

361
00:23:50,859 --> 00:23:54,280
And would they have become
Zhongxiao Pavilion's next targets?

362
00:24:00,779 --> 00:24:02,432
Just by closing the embroidery shop,

363
00:24:02,432 --> 00:24:04,425
such a big change has occurred.

364
00:24:04,425 --> 00:24:07,667
If we completely eradicate
the power of Zhongxiao Pavilion...

365
00:24:08,339 --> 00:24:10,780
what would happen then?

366
00:24:24,819 --> 00:24:26,779
If we give up now,

367
00:24:26,779 --> 00:24:27,779
perhaps,

368
00:24:27,779 --> 00:24:29,420
in a matter of time,

369
00:24:29,420 --> 00:24:32,620
this Ruzhen Embroidery Shop
would be kidnapping people in broad daylight.

370
00:24:32,620 --> 00:24:36,059
Zhongxiao Pavilion wouldn't need
Fenglai Pavilion as a cover anymore.

371
00:24:36,059 --> 00:24:39,140
They could operate openly on the street.

372
00:24:39,140 --> 00:24:40,380
I believe

373
00:24:40,380 --> 00:24:44,539
Constable Liu and Fan must have considered

374
00:24:44,539 --> 00:24:46,420
that they might fail.

375
00:24:46,420 --> 00:24:49,272
But they still went ahead because they believed

376
00:24:49,272 --> 00:24:52,259
that someone would continue
to investigate this case.

377
00:24:52,259 --> 00:24:53,900
That someone...

378
00:24:53,900 --> 00:24:56,417
would eventually get justice.

379
00:25:00,220 --> 00:25:02,100
When you took this case,

380
00:25:02,100 --> 00:25:06,492
you weren't certain that it would end with you,
were you?

381
00:25:10,499 --> 00:25:12,780
For the two of them,

382
00:25:12,780 --> 00:25:14,620
this justice...

383
00:25:14,620 --> 00:25:16,140
came too late.

384
00:25:16,140 --> 00:25:18,138
But for the common people,

385
00:25:18,138 --> 00:25:20,867
it's never too late.

386
00:25:28,300 --> 00:25:30,020
Your inner conflict is resolved,

387
00:25:30,020 --> 00:25:32,023
but I still have one.

388
00:25:32,023 --> 00:25:33,339
What is it?

389
00:25:33,339 --> 00:25:35,305
It's Bai.

390
00:25:36,340 --> 00:25:39,620
I feel like his recent actions
are a bit strange.

391
00:25:39,620 --> 00:25:40,940
Before he left,

392
00:25:40,940 --> 00:25:42,460
did he say anything to you?

393
00:25:42,460 --> 00:25:44,820
Bai Yu Tang said...

394
00:25:44,820 --> 00:25:46,579
he wanted to be a Yaksha.

395
00:25:46,579 --> 00:25:49,500
Purge all injustice with his sword.

396
00:25:49,500 --> 00:25:51,542
He also said...

397
00:25:55,540 --> 00:25:57,305
Forget it.

398
00:26:01,540 --> 00:26:02,873
Though Bai Yu Tang and I...

399
00:26:02,873 --> 00:26:05,420
haven't known each other long,

400
00:26:06,420 --> 00:26:09,255
he has already become a true friend to me.

401
00:26:09,255 --> 00:26:11,092
So, when Bai Yu Tang...

402
00:26:11,092 --> 00:26:13,220
said those things,

403
00:26:13,220 --> 00:26:15,292
to me...

404
00:26:20,155 --> 00:26:23,055
Bai was lying.

405
00:26:26,660 --> 00:26:28,605
Huo Xiao Mei!

406
00:26:32,100 --> 00:26:35,819
Do you know why I had you follow Zhan Zhao
to find that clerk?

407
00:26:35,819 --> 00:26:36,859
Why?

408
00:26:36,859 --> 00:26:40,859
Because that clerk might be one of
those responsible for Liu Hong Yi's death.

409
00:26:40,859 --> 00:26:43,540
And Zhan Zhao is Liu Hong Yi's
sworn brother.

410
00:26:43,540 --> 00:26:47,539
I was afraid that once he knew the truth,
he would act on impulse.

411
00:26:47,539 --> 00:26:49,940
That clerk's life is worthless,
he deserves to die.

412
00:26:49,940 --> 00:26:51,819
But Zhan Zhao works for the government.

413
00:26:51,819 --> 00:26:55,367
If he were to face charges for such a man,
wouldn't it be a waste?

414
00:26:56,660 --> 00:26:58,805
I understand.

415
00:27:01,099 --> 00:27:04,779
I think he was just blinded by rage
at what He Bo had done.

416
00:27:04,779 --> 00:27:06,900
That's why he spoke so recklessly.

417
00:27:06,900 --> 00:27:09,539
As for the Yaksha matter...

418
00:27:10,539 --> 00:27:11,819
I think...

419
00:27:11,819 --> 00:27:14,080
Bai acted out of indignation.

420
00:27:14,900 --> 00:27:18,393
He is desperate to right the wrongs
and restore justice in Xiangzhou.

421
00:27:18,393 --> 00:27:20,180
Indignation aside,

422
00:27:20,180 --> 00:27:23,692
the path of the Yaksha
is one that must never be taken.

423
00:27:26,140 --> 00:27:29,059
I've heard many rumors about
the Yaksha on my way here.

424
00:27:29,059 --> 00:27:32,467
People say he is a hero
who punishes evil and eliminates villains.

425
00:27:33,140 --> 00:27:35,567
If he were a hero,

426
00:27:35,567 --> 00:27:37,379
why would his statue be in Zhongxiao Pavilion,

427
00:27:37,379 --> 00:27:40,019
guarding the gates for the wicked?

428
00:27:40,019 --> 00:27:41,700
When the Yaksha first appeared,

429
00:27:41,700 --> 00:27:46,180
he did intend to use his sword
to wipe out all injustice in the world.

430
00:27:46,180 --> 00:27:47,900
But can right and wrong

431
00:27:47,900 --> 00:27:49,859
be decided by one person's judgment?

432
00:27:49,859 --> 00:27:51,820
When there is too much killing,

433
00:27:51,820 --> 00:27:54,622
and he can no longer tell if the sword is drawn
for justice

434
00:27:54,622 --> 00:27:57,460
or for the thrill of playing god,

435
00:27:57,460 --> 00:28:00,340
how can he distinguish...

436
00:28:00,340 --> 00:28:02,339
whether the Yaksha's existence...

437
00:28:02,339 --> 00:28:05,755
is right or wrong?

438
00:28:14,980 --> 00:28:16,900
Zhan,

439
00:28:16,900 --> 00:28:18,717
you seem...

440
00:28:18,717 --> 00:28:21,467
to know a lot about the stories of the Yaksha.

441
00:28:23,859 --> 00:28:26,105
I've heard others speak of it.

442
00:28:32,379 --> 00:28:34,966
But you were right just now.

443
00:28:35,539 --> 00:28:38,619
Though Bai Yu Tang is hot-tempered
and impulsive,

444
00:28:38,619 --> 00:28:40,859
his anger usually passes after a short while.

445
00:28:40,859 --> 00:28:42,940
He is rarely like this,

446
00:28:42,940 --> 00:28:45,859
acting without considering any consequences.

447
00:28:45,859 --> 00:28:48,500
I fear there is more to this.

448
00:28:48,500 --> 00:28:49,900
Let's go.

449
00:28:49,900 --> 00:28:51,539
- We should go to--
- Wait a moment.

450
00:28:51,539 --> 00:28:53,883
The sun is about to rise.

451
00:29:28,460 --> 00:29:30,379
Zhi Hua's Great Compassion Palm,

452
00:29:30,379 --> 00:29:32,099
and what happened to the Ding family...

453
00:29:32,099 --> 00:29:33,705
I suspect...

454
00:29:33,705 --> 00:29:37,170
Zhongxiao Pavilion and Jing Yi Ming
are inextricably linked.

455
00:29:37,900 --> 00:29:40,133
He Bo is the Master of the Shangqing Sect,

456
00:29:40,133 --> 00:29:42,117
Jing Yi Ming.

457
00:29:44,513 --> 00:29:47,180
What a sanctimonious titan.

458
00:29:47,180 --> 00:29:48,779
But we have no evidence.

459
00:29:48,779 --> 00:29:51,135
How can we convict him?

460
00:29:51,135 --> 00:29:52,580
The Yicheng County Magistrate said

461
00:29:52,580 --> 00:29:54,859
the rule of concealing guests' identities
at Zhongxiao Pavilion

462
00:29:54,859 --> 00:29:57,180
is a facade for the officials.

463
00:29:57,180 --> 00:29:58,539
He Bo has...

464
00:29:58,539 --> 00:30:02,717
a ledger specifically for recording
dealings with officials.

465
00:30:04,220 --> 00:30:06,759
So, if we can get that ledger,

466
00:30:06,759 --> 00:30:09,260
then the corrupt officials in Xiangzhou
can be rooted out.

467
00:30:09,260 --> 00:30:10,700
Yes.

468
00:30:10,700 --> 00:30:12,532
If the officials on the ledger

469
00:30:12,532 --> 00:30:14,299
and the girls in Zhongxiao Pavilion

470
00:30:14,299 --> 00:30:16,220
have seen He Bo's true face,

471
00:30:16,220 --> 00:30:19,220
they can serve as witnesses
to testify against him.

472
00:30:19,220 --> 00:30:21,020
Then He Bo's crimes

473
00:30:21,020 --> 00:30:23,471
can be revealed to the world.

474
00:30:24,220 --> 00:30:25,740
That's great.

475
00:30:25,740 --> 00:30:27,980
The officials in Zhongxiao Pavilion...

476
00:30:27,980 --> 00:30:30,392
the missing martial artists...

477
00:30:30,392 --> 00:30:32,140
Where exactly is Yu Lian?

478
00:30:32,140 --> 00:30:34,539
Has she seen He Bo's true face?

479
00:30:34,539 --> 00:30:36,220
We don't know any of this yet.

480
00:30:36,220 --> 00:30:37,660
Zhongxiao Pavilion...

481
00:30:37,660 --> 00:30:39,955
We must go there once more.

482
00:30:41,500 --> 00:30:43,099
But right now,

483
00:30:43,099 --> 00:30:44,859
they must have tightened security.

484
00:30:44,859 --> 00:30:46,460
I'm afraid it won't be easy to get in.

485
00:30:46,460 --> 00:30:48,655
Perhaps there's another way.

486
00:30:48,655 --> 00:30:50,140
I discovered something today.

487
00:30:50,140 --> 00:30:51,819
In front of Miss Hui Dai's grave,

488
00:30:51,819 --> 00:30:54,567
there's a new nameless headstone.

489
00:31:08,220 --> 00:31:09,859
In Zhongxiao Pavilion,

490
00:31:09,859 --> 00:31:12,879
they gave you the name Hui Dai.

491
00:31:13,579 --> 00:31:15,367
But I thought...

492
00:31:15,367 --> 00:31:18,505
you wouldn't want that name on your headstone.

493
00:31:18,505 --> 00:31:21,099
So I set up a nameless one for you.

494
00:31:21,099 --> 00:31:24,019
Once I find out your real name,

495
00:31:24,019 --> 00:31:26,430
I will add it for you.

496
00:31:33,499 --> 00:31:35,060
As a fellow woman,

497
00:31:35,060 --> 00:31:36,901
you saw her being humiliated every day,

498
00:31:36,901 --> 00:31:39,605
yet you had to obey He Bo.

499
00:31:39,605 --> 00:31:41,259
In your heart...

500
00:31:41,259 --> 00:31:43,060
you must have been suffering as well.

501
00:31:43,060 --> 00:31:44,860
What choice do we have?

502
00:31:44,860 --> 00:31:46,900
He Bo and his death squad's moves

503
00:31:46,900 --> 00:31:48,540
perfectly counter our Hanshui Palace.

504
00:31:48,540 --> 00:31:50,660
With Chang Hong Bi in their hands,

505
00:31:50,660 --> 00:31:53,060
we are forced to be under his control.

506
00:31:54,060 --> 00:31:55,459
If there were a chance...

507
00:31:55,459 --> 00:31:57,860
to escape He Bo's clutches,

508
00:31:57,860 --> 00:32:00,742
would you be willing to take the risk?

509
00:32:04,380 --> 00:32:07,019
I, Zhan Zhao, venture to ask the Moon Envoy.

510
00:32:07,019 --> 00:32:08,660
Help us re-enter Zhongxiao Pavilion.

511
00:32:08,660 --> 00:32:12,739
If we can take down He Bo and rescue
the suffering girls in Zhongxiao Pavilion,

512
00:32:12,739 --> 00:32:15,680
it will also free Hanshui Palace.

513
00:32:22,219 --> 00:32:24,842
Zhongxiao Pavilion reopens tonight.

514
00:32:25,420 --> 00:32:29,180
Now is the perfect time to
re-enter Zhongxiao Pavilion.

515
00:32:29,180 --> 00:32:32,499
But to uncover all the secrets
of Zhongxiao Pavilion,

516
00:32:32,499 --> 00:32:35,292
just entering the underground palace
is far from enough.

517
00:32:48,019 --> 00:32:51,219
I am aware of the situation
regarding my two elder brothers.

518
00:32:51,219 --> 00:32:52,900
The antidote will be obtained soon.

519
00:32:52,900 --> 00:32:55,017
Do not worry, everyone.

520
00:33:01,642 --> 00:33:03,460
Sir.

521
00:33:03,460 --> 00:33:04,740
Same as last time,

522
00:33:04,740 --> 00:33:06,580
deliver it to Xiankong Island,
Songjiang Prefecture.

523
00:33:06,580 --> 00:33:09,080
Understood. Rest assured.

524
00:33:25,539 --> 00:33:27,019
- You stay here.
- I'm going too.

525
00:33:27,019 --> 00:33:29,500
I knew you would say that.

526
00:33:29,500 --> 00:33:32,745
From the moment the Moon Envoy said
how dangerous the secret chamber was,

527
00:33:32,745 --> 00:33:34,900
- you've been planning this, haven't you?
- It's dangerous.

528
00:33:34,900 --> 00:33:37,380
It's dangerous, so I must go with you.

529
00:33:37,380 --> 00:33:39,999
With me by your side,
I can at least look out for you.

530
00:33:39,999 --> 00:33:41,219
No.

531
00:33:41,219 --> 00:33:42,580
Since you know it's dangerous,

532
00:33:42,580 --> 00:33:44,380
why should we both take the risk?

533
00:33:44,380 --> 00:33:46,539
If something were to happen to me,

534
00:33:46,539 --> 00:33:49,459
someone must remain
to continue the investigation.

535
00:33:49,459 --> 00:33:50,919
Don't you want the same thing as me,

536
00:33:50,919 --> 00:33:53,630
to rescue those girls?

537
00:34:01,180 --> 00:34:02,755
That's not right.

538
00:34:02,755 --> 00:34:05,305
You almost talked me into a corner.

539
00:34:05,305 --> 00:34:06,839
I'm not part of the government.

540
00:34:06,839 --> 00:34:08,302
Why would I be investigating a case?

541
00:34:08,302 --> 00:34:09,540
But you,

542
00:34:09,540 --> 00:34:11,060
you are the one with the imperial decree.

543
00:34:11,060 --> 00:34:14,830
I must ensure your safety
so that this case can be solved properly.

544
00:34:16,340 --> 00:34:18,605
I'm afraid that with you following me...

545
00:34:18,605 --> 00:34:21,755
I won't be as focused as if I were alone.

546
00:34:25,019 --> 00:34:27,219
You're even more blunt than Shao Ji Zu.

547
00:34:27,219 --> 00:34:28,580
You think I'm a burden,

548
00:34:28,580 --> 00:34:31,130
and you say it so openly.

549
00:34:31,130 --> 00:34:32,459
I...

550
00:34:32,459 --> 00:34:34,730
How could I mean that?

551
00:34:34,730 --> 00:34:38,691
I meant, if you come with me,
I will be constantly worried about you.

552
00:34:38,691 --> 00:34:40,680
Do you understand?

553
00:34:48,699 --> 00:34:50,331
A...

554
00:34:51,140 --> 00:34:53,580
A little bit.

555
00:34:58,140 --> 00:34:59,700
Then I'll wait in the shop's backyard.

556
00:34:59,700 --> 00:35:02,267
That is my final offer.

557
00:35:04,380 --> 00:35:06,880
Thank you, Master Huo.

558
00:36:15,060 --> 00:36:17,198
Zhi Hua knew you would come tonight.

559
00:36:17,198 --> 00:36:19,555
He is waiting for you inside.

560
00:36:36,005 --> 00:36:37,680
Give me the medicine.

561
00:36:38,339 --> 00:36:41,917
Give me the medicine.

562
00:36:48,180 --> 00:36:50,660
Give me the medicine.

563
00:36:50,660 --> 00:36:52,820
Give me the medicine.

564
00:36:53,820 --> 00:36:54,940
Give me the medicine.

565
00:36:54,940 --> 00:36:56,692
Give me the medicine.

566
00:36:56,692 --> 00:36:58,259
Give me the medicine.

567
00:36:58,259 --> 00:37:00,500
Hurry, give me the medicine.

568
00:37:00,500 --> 00:37:01,992
Give me the medicine.

569
00:37:02,620 --> 00:37:03,859
Give me the medicine.

570
00:37:03,859 --> 00:37:07,219
I was afraid you weren't aware of
your sworn brothers' current state.

571
00:37:07,219 --> 00:37:09,859
So I brought you here to see for yourself.

572
00:37:10,859 --> 00:37:16,005
I want you to see what happens
when the Yemotian poison takes effect.

573
00:37:22,660 --> 00:37:25,055
Master Bai is indeed unyielding.

574
00:37:25,055 --> 00:37:27,299
Coming here with such aggression...

575
00:37:27,299 --> 00:37:29,060
You don't look like you're begging.

576
00:37:29,060 --> 00:37:32,742
It seems you're here to take my life.

577
00:37:45,020 --> 00:37:47,140
You gave me a few lashes back then.

578
00:37:47,140 --> 00:37:49,286
I will return the favor in full today!

579
00:37:49,286 --> 00:37:51,830
As long as you hand over the antidote,

580
00:37:51,830 --> 00:37:55,699
you can do whatever you want with me.

581
00:37:55,699 --> 00:37:58,060
Master Bai is such a talent.

582
00:37:58,060 --> 00:38:01,117
It would be a pity to kill you.

583
00:38:03,020 --> 00:38:06,540
Since you won't stay by Zhan Zhao's side
to gather information for me,

584
00:38:06,540 --> 00:38:09,005
I won't force you.

585
00:38:15,379 --> 00:38:16,867
Drink this.

586
00:38:17,460 --> 00:38:19,259
Go kill someone for me.

587
00:38:19,259 --> 00:38:23,280
Afterward, I will give you the antidote.

588
00:38:31,817 --> 00:38:32,859
Don't worry.

589
00:38:32,859 --> 00:38:35,540
I won't ask you to kill the innocent.

590
00:38:35,540 --> 00:38:39,140
Zhan Zhao doesn't appreciate
your chivalrous heart,

591
00:38:39,140 --> 00:38:41,755
but I am happy to help you fulfill it.

592
00:38:55,580 --> 00:38:59,779
If Bai Yu Tang finds out
that there is no antidote for Yemotian,

593
00:38:59,779 --> 00:39:03,010
he might turn back to find Zhan Zhao.

594
00:39:03,010 --> 00:39:04,940
That is why...

595
00:39:04,940 --> 00:39:09,779
before he learns the truth,
we must make sure he can't turn back.

596
00:39:09,779 --> 00:39:12,620
The one you want him to kill is
the Yicheng County Magistrate?

597
00:39:12,620 --> 00:39:14,480
Exactly.

598
00:39:15,500 --> 00:39:17,219
Zhan Zhao wants to protect him,

599
00:39:17,219 --> 00:39:19,192
so I'll have Bai Yu Tang kill him.

600
00:39:19,192 --> 00:39:22,259
The two will surely clash
again over this matter.

601
00:39:22,259 --> 00:39:24,460
In all the martial arts world,

602
00:39:24,460 --> 00:39:27,540
there are few who can rival Zhan Zhao.

603
00:39:27,540 --> 00:39:29,460
Bai Yu Tang is one of them.

604
00:39:29,460 --> 00:39:32,260
I am truly curious to see
if the two of them fight,

605
00:39:32,260 --> 00:39:34,899
who will ultimately win.

606
00:39:34,899 --> 00:39:37,060
If they fight each other,

607
00:39:37,060 --> 00:39:40,779
no matter who gets hurt,
it will be of immense benefit to me.

608
00:39:40,779 --> 00:39:42,660
That Bai Yu Tang...

609
00:39:42,660 --> 00:39:44,540
he is quite shrewd.

610
00:39:44,540 --> 00:39:46,739
If he figures out the trick,

611
00:39:46,739 --> 00:39:48,620
I'm afraid he won't act.

612
00:39:48,620 --> 00:39:51,660
Don't worry, he will definitely kill him.

613
00:39:51,660 --> 00:39:55,100
By then, killing him won't even
be enough to satisfy his hatred.

614
00:39:55,100 --> 00:39:58,460
He will want to tear him limb from limb.

615
00:39:58,460 --> 00:40:01,699
Si Ming sent someone to inform me of something.

616
00:40:01,699 --> 00:40:04,580
He said Bai Yu Tang and this magistrate...

617
00:40:04,580 --> 00:40:07,255
actually have quite a history.

618
00:40:08,851 --> 00:40:10,219
15 years ago,

619
00:40:10,219 --> 00:40:14,620
the Yicheng County Magistrate was a clerk
at the Tanxi Town county government office.

620
00:40:14,620 --> 00:40:20,620
There was a major case that everyone knew about
and passed through his hands.

621
00:40:48,379 --> 00:40:50,299
Bai Yu Tang.

622
00:40:50,299 --> 00:40:52,217
Who hurt you?

623
00:40:54,620 --> 00:40:56,767
It's none of your business.

624
00:41:01,180 --> 00:41:03,460
Where did you hide
the Yicheng County Magistrate?

625
00:41:03,460 --> 00:41:05,739
Are you really determined to work for Zhi Hua?

626
00:41:05,739 --> 00:41:08,019
Where did you hide
the Yicheng County Magistrate?

627
00:41:08,019 --> 00:41:09,680
Bai Yu Tang.

628
00:41:09,680 --> 00:41:12,414
Don't do something you can't turn back from.

629
00:41:13,299 --> 00:41:14,884
Fine.

630
00:41:15,739 --> 00:41:17,407
If you won't tell me,

631
00:41:18,140 --> 00:41:20,692
I'll find him myself.

632
00:41:26,299 --> 00:41:29,367
Let's go. Don't let anyone see us.

633
00:42:02,980 --> 00:42:05,013
I spiked the water I gave to the guard.

634
00:42:05,013 --> 00:42:06,580
He won't be coming around soon.

635
00:42:06,580 --> 00:42:09,399
Once you go in,
I will stand guard at the door for you.

636
00:42:09,399 --> 00:42:10,779
Fu Feng.

637
00:42:10,779 --> 00:42:13,292
Thank you for taking the risk to help me.
